zugleich eine territorialisierbare Raum-Zeit, welche eine ungeheure Mannigfaltigkeit an literarischen Entwicklungen nicht allein in den romanischen Literaturen Europas, sondern auch weiter Gebiete der außereuropäischen Welt miteinschließt.  aThis lecture presents an overview of the world's Romance literatures on their journey from the historic avant-gardes of the early twentieth century to the literatures following postmodernity at the beginning of our century. It thus captures a historic time-space that envelops an entire century, and also a space-time that encompasses a tremendous diversity of literary developments.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aRomance-language literaturey20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aHistorische Avantgarden. 4aLiteraturen der Welt. 4aRomanische Literaturen. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh  aRomance literatures.  ahistorical avant-gardes.  aworld literatures.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021z9783110753899oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831107035110 cprintz978311070333740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110703450zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110703450zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110703450/original  a978-3-11-075070-6 DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DKUb2021  aZDB-23-GOA